352
00:47:57,360 --> 00:47:58,560
Ég fékk hana.

353
00:47:58,640 --> 00:47:59,520
Frábært.

354
00:48:00,640 --> 00:48:03,800
Mig langar að kíkja í bókabúðina.

355
00:48:04,560 --> 00:48:05,760
Viltu koma með?

356
00:48:07,720 --> 00:48:08,600
Endilega.

357
00:48:16,920 --> 00:48:17,960
Hann notar hann.

358
